"bundle-data": {Bundle mLACP TLV counter information

            
"iccp-group-id": "integer", ICCP Group ID

            
"mlacp-sync-requests-on-all-local-ports": {Counts of mLACP sync request TLVs on all ports

              
"received-sync-requests": {Number of mLACP sync request TLVs received

                
"config-syncs": "integer", Number of config sync requests received

                
"all-syncs": "integer", Total number of sync requests received

                
"state-syncs": "integer" Number of state sync requests received

              },

            },

          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
